cbhatia2.bio:
Hello. My name is Curran, and I am from Cupertino, California.  Living in 
 Silicon Valley for my entire life, I've always been surrounded by technology, 
 and always wanted to be a part of the world-changing culture. I am inspired 
 by the fact that companies like Twitter and Facebook, have the power 
 to bring people together and cause drastic change in the world; 
 it is awe inspiring, and something I want to be a part of.  
 Through UIUC's Computer Science program, I hope to gain the knowledge in order to work 
 in start ups, and eventually become a successful tech entrepreneur.
cbhatia2.name: Curran Bhatia

stillot2.bio: I am new to computer science entirely and am grateful to have had this experience thus far.  I joined this class in order to get a better idea about the environment and lifestyle of CS and have been very impressed.  I would recommend CS196 to anyone and everyone who would like to explore a career in Computer Science.
stillot2.name: Sean Tillotson
